{"tid":309953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"敍利亞民主軍突破舊城區城牆 拉卡收復指日可待","createTime":"2017-07-05T12:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T15:58:58.000Z","uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7da58f17e2c4a1f6ab8cbef5083faa11bbcde37f","tid":309953,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T12:29:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170704/56914262\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170704%2F56914262&d=av5Zn%2Bsyom2N2kpo%2B3Jt3ywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=a6fca3e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170704%2F56914262&h=803e5cd7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170704/56914262</a><br />\n<br />\n 極端組織「伊斯蘭國」（IS）在伊拉克勢力大減後，位於敍利亞的據點也岌岌可危。在美國為首的盟軍幫助下，其支持的敍利亞武裝部隊炸開舊城區城牆，陸續攻入IS大本營拉卡中心地帶。美國官員形容這是剿滅IS戰事的「里程碑」。<br />\n<br />\n美軍中央司令部周二指出，在盟軍空襲掩護下，敍利亞反對派武裝部隊在拉卡東南面的拉斐卡牆（Rafiqah Wall）打開兩個缺口，成功進入舊城區，牆身大部分結構完好無損。IS分子激烈反抗，佈下大量地雷並發動炸彈襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n庫爾德部隊上月起已先後攻入拉卡附近各個鄉郊地區，反對派武裝亦花了數月時間從東西兩面接近拉卡，周日更越過拉卡南端的幼發拉底河，對IS形成包圍之勢。分析指出，今次突破拉斐卡牆是拉卡之戰的重要進展，部隊即將迎來與IS的正面交鋒。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，目前正部署在地中海的美軍航母「布殊號」一名軍官指出，由於與敍利亞政府關係緊張，對當地局勢非常警覺。軍方已預留一小部分戰力，準備好隨時攻擊敍軍，以確保盟友安全。"},{"pid":"b4173d291c12b0aebfe144a42afb9c3e788c58f4","tid":309953,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T12:32:59.000Z","msg":"伊拉克庫德斯坦就快獨立公投<br />\n敍利亞庫爾德人領導滅isis<br />\n會唔會好快有中東清泉大庫德斯坦國成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/MuGBShGSQ9Q/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FMuGBShGSQ9Q%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=3cccfd05&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be73110bf519f7f2f423ac52c308fc1814171b74","tid":309953,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffa7a5d20f2f0ef80388a978e0e59a6c0908de6","tid":309953,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T14:45:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>伊拉克庫德斯坦就快獨立公投<br />\n敍利亞庫爾德人領導滅isis<br />\n會唔會好快有中東清泉大庫德斯坦國成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/MuGBShGSQ9Q/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FMuGBShGSQ9Q%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=3cccfd05&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n庫爾德人好親美親西方<br />\n如果庫爾德斯坦真係立國，美國應該會好高興"},{"pid":"2222481e8fb7577f953a69a895c872fbccf53d47","tid":309953,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T15:58:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>伊拉克庫德斯坦就快獨立公投<br />\n敍利亞庫爾德人領導滅isis<br />\n會唔會好快有中東清泉大庫德斯坦國成立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/MuGBShGSQ9Q/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FMuGBShGSQ9Q%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=3cccfd05&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n庫爾德人好親美親西方<br />\n如果庫爾德斯坦真係立國，美國應該會好高興</blockquote><br />\n伊拉克Kurds就係伊戰時Peshmerga全力支持美軍, 喺伊拉克個地盤先至咁穩, 重有條件搞獨立公投<br />\n敍利亞Kurds而家情形都有啲似, 反isis最重要嘅民主軍就係佢地為主, 變相同美國結成聯盟. 但民主軍個底本身係工人黨, 土耳其視為勢不兩立, 中間夾住個nato火雞, 美國未必可以支持得佢地太盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}